        "enrichmentDataCollection": "<p>User Groups being created then added to privileged groups</p><p></p><h1><span style=\"color:#6888C9;\"><b>Group account added to built-in domain local or global group</b></span></h1><p><b>Purpose</b>:</p><p>Identifies when a recently created Group was added to a privileged built-in domain local group or global group such as the Enterprise Admins, Cert Publishers or DnsAdmins.  Be sure to verify this is an expected addition.</p><p><b>Potential Log Sources</b>: SecurityEvents </p><p><b>Events of interest</b>: SecurityEvent</p><p><b>Logs Collection prerequisites</b>:</p><p>Windows logs with Event ID:</p><ul>\n<li><p><b><span style=\"color:#E67300;background-color:#F6F6F6;\">4727: A security-enabled global group was created</span></b></p></li>\n<li><p><b><span style=\"color:#E67300;background-color:#F6F6F6;\">4731: A security-enabled local group was created</span></b></p></li>\n<li><p><b><span style=\"color:#E67300;background-color:#F6F6F6;\">4754: A security-enabled universal group was created</span></b></p></li>\n</ul>",
