        "killChain": [
          "Exploitation"
        ],
        "automationMaturity": "Partially automated",
        "detectionSourceLogic": "<p>Monitor windows event logs</p><p>focus on 2 event ID's</p><ul>\n<li><p>4720: A user account was created </p></li>\n<li><p>4723: An attempt was made to change an account's password</p></li>\n</ul><p>SIEM rule:</p><p>Window event ID 4720 detected, </p><p>list </p><ul>\n<li><p>date\\time</p></li>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:black;background-color:#F6F6F6;\">Security ID: xxxxxx</span></p></li>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:black;\"><span style=\"background-color:#F6F6F6;\">Account Name: xxxxxx</span></span></p></li>\n</ul><p><span style=\"color:black;background-color:#F6F6F6;\">In Window event ID 4720</span></p><p>Start timer task 48 hours</p><p>If </p><p>Window event ID 4723 detected</p><p>With </p><ul>\n<li><p>Security ID: xxxxxx</p></li>\n<li><p>Account Name: xxxxxx</p></li>\n</ul><p>= values in list of Window event ID 4720</p><p>Then delete list</p><p></p><p>If </p><p>Window event ID not 4723 detected</p><p>With </p><ul>\n<li><p>Security ID: xxxxxx</p></li>\n<li><p>Account Name: xxxxxx</p></li>\n</ul><p>= values in list of Window event ID 4720</p><p></p><p>Create Alert</p>",
        "enrichmentDataCollection": "<p>Determine what account created the user account that did not change password</p><p>What user accounts do not have a password</p><p>What were the activities related to the user account that did not change password</p><p>See attached list to collect information</p><ul>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:#313131;\">Who Created a User Account in Active Directory</span></p></li>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:#313131;\">W</span>hich accounts do not have a password set</p></li>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:black;\">Active Directory Password not Required </span></p></li>\n<li><p>List of Recently Created Users in Active Directory</p></li>\n</ul><p></p><ul>\n<li><p><b>Purpose</b>: </p></li>\n<li><p>Identifies whenever a new account is created with a default password and password is not changed within 24-48 hours. </p></li>\n<li><p><b>Potential Log Sources</b>: SecurityEvents </p></li>\n<li><p><b>Events of interest</b>: SecurityEvent</p></li>\n<li><p>Microsoft Event IDs to be checked: </p></li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/security/threat-protection/auditing/event-4720\"><u><span style=\"color:#1155CC;\">4720</span></u></a><u><span style=\"color:#1155CC;\"> - New user-created </span></u></p></li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/security/threat-protection/auditing/event-4722\"><u><span style=\"color:#1155CC;\">4722</span></u></a> - User account enabled</p></li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/security/threat-protection/auditing/event-4723\"><u><span style=\"color:#1155CC;\">4723</span></u></a> - An attempt was made to change an account's password. </p></li>\n<li><p>Check if the user is created newly by checking Event ID<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/security/threat-protection/auditing/event-4720\"><u><span style=\"color:#1155CC;\"> 4720</span></u></a>. User Account Control flag values for a newly created account is</p></li>\n<li style=\"list-style-type:none;\"><ul>\n<li><p>%%2080 - (account disabled )</p></li>\n<li><p>%%2082 - (‘Password not required ‘ - Enabled )</p></li>\n<li><p>%%2084 - (’Normal account’ - Enabled) </p></li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
