        "detectionSourceLogic": "<p><b><span style=\"color:#D50000;\">Did not find a direct MITRE reference, input from the other analyst welcome</span></b></p><p></p><p>Alerts from <span style=\"color:#032F62;\">antivirus product detection of a virus  in a highly relevant file path or with a relevant file name. </span></p><p>Alert\\events sent to SIEM</p><p>SIEM Rule: (Sigma rules)</p><p>FileName=\"C:\\Windows\\Temp\\*\" OR FileName=\"C:\\Temp\\*\" OR FileName=\"*\\Client\\*\" OR FileName=\"C:\\PerfLogs\\*\" OR FileName=\"C:\\Users\\Public\\*\" OR FileName=\"C:\\Users\\Default\\*\" OR FileName=\"*.ps1\" OR FileName=\"*.vbs\" OR FileName=\"*.bat\" OR FileName=\"*.chm\" OR FileName=\"*.xml\" OR FileName=\"*.txt\" OR FileName=\"*.jsp\" OR FileName=\"*.jspx\" OR FileName=\"*.asp\" OR FileName=\"*.aspx\" OR FileName=\"*.php\" OR FileName=\"*.war\" OR FileName=\"*.hta\" OR FileName=\"*.lnk\" OR FileName=\"*.scf\" OR FileName=\"*.sct\" OR FileName=\"*.vbe\" OR FileName=\"*.wsf\" OR FileName=\"*.wsh\")</p>",
        "enrichmentDataCollection": "<p>In addition to the Antivirus events and correlated events (Alert) from the SIEM other sources data should be collected in relation to activity from the Host. </p><p>Check other activity related to the Host system: IPS, url filter, Email Gateway, EDR, Etc to include in the investigation</p>",
