        "detectionSourceLogic": "<p>MS-A003 Query (standard MS query)</p><p>Multiple Querys define the detection</p><ol>\n<li><p>Setup baseline of location for each login to Azure Active Directory</p></li>\n<li><p>Identify anomaly of signin location (per user per AD)- Alert</p></li>\n</ol><p> - connectorId: AzureActiveDirectory dataTypes: - SigninLogs</p>",
